#

Beef Tenderloin Salad with Balsamic Vinaigrette

30 min
$20
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSalad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickBeef

Description

A fresh and hearty salad featuring tender beef, crisp greens, and a tangy balsamic vinaigrette that brings everything together beautifully.

Ingredients

  • beef tenderloin: 1 pound
  • mixed salad greens: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1, sliced
  • red onion: 1/4, thinly sliced
  • balsamic vinegar: 3 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
